"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-25-paris-olympics-football-its-a-disgrace-mascherano-reacts-as-morocco-beat-argentina-2-1\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Argentina U2 manager, Javier Mascherano has reacted to his team's defeat to Morocco in their opening game of the Paris 2024 Olympics football events.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 3.829457619264026e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U2\", \"score\": 0.999997616726771, \"rank\": 2.3832727341105464e-06, \"text\": \"U2\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U2\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U2\"}, {\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Mascherano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998747171, \"rank\": 1.2515219273385404e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The coach was particularly concerned about La Albiceleste's late equalizer which was ruled out by VAR.\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1031928347289204e-25, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match ended in a 2-1 defeat for the 2024 Copa America champions on July 24, 2024, at Geoffroy-Guichard Stadium in France.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.284553857259877e-14, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Africans were 2-1 up at the end of 90 minutes and officials added a 15-minute injury time.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the added time, Cristian Medina scored a late equalizer for Argentina, which would have ended the match in a 2-2 draw.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cristian Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 3.829457619264026e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the game was interrupted as angry Moroccan fans entered the stadium.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7486604163008903e-15, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match was temporarily suspended and after about two hours, a VAR check ruled out Argentina's equalizer, declaring it to be offside.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1031928347289204e-25, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}, {\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 3.829457619264026e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the situation was under control, the remaining three-plus minutes were played as players re-emerged in an empty stadium.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The clash finally ended in a 2-1 win for Morocco.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998747171, \"rank\": 1.2515219273385404e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mascherano said (via @AlbicelesteTalk on X): \\\"The biggest circus I have ever seen in my life.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know what happened.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were in the locker room for almost an hour and a half.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At no point were we informed about what could happen.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a player, I have never experienced security failing seven times in a match at this level.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a disgrace.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today, they invaded the pitch seven times and then threw fireworks at us.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They told us the match finished 2-2.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither we nor Morocco wanted to continue playing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998747171, \"rank\": 1.2515219273385404e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Olympics football: Nothing like this ever happened - Otamendi reacts as Morocco beat Argentina  Champions League: Mourinho slams UEFA after Fenerbahce's 4-3 win over Lugano  AFCON: CAF dividing Africa - Senegal's Gueye speaks on returning gold medals to 